Maintainer: Sam Protsenko <joe.skb7@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11), dpkg-dev (>= 1.16.1~), pkg-config,
 cmake (>= 2.6.0), liblua5.1-0-dev, zlib1g-dev, libgtk2.0-dev,
